<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN233-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. vēḷ evviyai veḷḷerukkilaiyār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN233">
      <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>poyyā kiyarō poyyā kiyarō</l>
<l>pāvaṭi yāṉaip paricilark karukāc</l>
<l>cīrkeḻu nōṉṟā ḷakutaikaṭ ṭōṉṟiya</l>
<l>poṉpuṉai tikiriyiṟ poyyā kiyarō</l>
<l>virumpā ṇokkaṟ ṟalaivaṉ perumpūṭ</l>
<l>pōraṭu tāṉai yevvi mārpi</l>
<l>ṉeḵkuṟu viḻuppuṇ palaveṉa</l>
<l>vaikuṟu viṭiya liyampiya kuralē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">  Let it be a lie! Let it be a lie! </l>
<l corresp="4ab">Like the gold-made discus </l>
<l corresp="3">that appeared before the eye of Akutai of excellent durable effort </l>
<l corresp="2">who is not stingy to mendicants with large-footed elephants, </l>
<l>	let it be a lie</l>
<l corresp="8">– the voice that anounced at the crack of dawn </l>
<l corresp="7">that the excellent wounds caused by blades are many </l>
<l corresp="6">in the chest of Evvi, with a army killing in battle, </l>
<l corresp="5">with big ornaments, leader of a big clan of bards. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
